metadata.name: Reborn
metadata.description:
The Queen of perseverance - Being caught up in a creative rut due to too much work and a very bad work life balance in the beginning of 2022 I finally felt like creating again - thatÂ´s how this Queen was born!
At the time I felt drained and empty and wasn't sure my creativity would come back but creating this piece gave me so much and I kept it close. 

Hope she'll help someone to feel inspired and believe in themselves again even though life is a little more tough than usual like she did for me!
